    ## Council Election
    
    The status of Council Elections. If this is the process of announcing, then the following information is sufficient:
    
    ### [**Election Round 18**](https://pioneerapp.xyz/#/election)
    
    - Election stage: **Announcing Period**
    - Candidates number: **0**
    
    If these are other stages, the following data should be provided:
    
    ### [*Election Round 17*](https://pioneerapp.xyz/#/election)
    
    - Election stage: Voting Period
    - Candidates number: 8
